rows.label: tlk70000119_05_msg0001
rows.name: I'll be setting off for Invidia soon.

rows.label: tlk70000119_05_msg0002
rows.name:
I haven't been able to say hello
to Rita-chan and Kaede-san yet.

rows.label: tlk70000119_05_msg0003
rows.name:
It's a bit out of my way, but
I think I'll go via Iira.

rows.label: tlk70000119_05_msg0004
rows.name:
Wouldn't feel right finishing up
here without seeing them again...

rows.label: tlk70000119_05_msg0005
rows.name:
Don't worry about me. I
can take care of myself.

rows.label: tlk70000119_05_msg0006
rows.name:
You've been good to me. Hope
I'll see you again in Invidia!
